Prompt in Week One for the discussion forum <b>Global Politics and You</b>: Post a link to a short news article that you think is good example of “G”lobalization and explain why you chose it. You are not limited to any particular kind of news or news source, just so long as it demonstrates the idea of “big G” Globalization.
<br>
<br>
The articles posted here are ones that you, the students!, have found and added to the discussion forum.

